{"word":"μεταλλεύω","slug":"μεταλλεύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>μεταλλεύω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>σω</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:μέταλλον'><el>μέταλλον</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to get by mining</i>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be got by mining</i>, of metals, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>generally, <i>to explore</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}